  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">End cruelty to bears in the bear bile industry</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Bears held in captivity for their bile across Asia endure a lifetime of intense physical and mental suffering. They are confined to tiny cages, unable to express their natural behaviours and forced to undergo torturously painful extractions - sometimes daily. We are raising public awareness, microchipping and monitoring captive bears and improving the legal protection of bears. Together, we can bring a permanent end to this cruel and unnecessary industry.</narrative>
  </description>
